* Iron Raptor sighed and looked around the empty conferance room, wondering 
just how far the resque team had gone, and if both Tavatron and Dinobot were 
alright.
They were the Maximals left under her charge, her care. And, believe it or 
not, she cared about each and every one of them. And would be sorry to hear 
if any of them had passed away or been seriously injured.
She looked arounf the room again before she suddenly heard a voice coming 
from behind her, from the direction of the door.
Iron Raptor half turned to see a feline bot standing there, one the looked 
strangely familier but she couldn't quite place where she had seen him 
before.
No matter. She would find out later.*

" Yes, I am. Can I help you?"
